value.0: This young man looks very worried and does not appear to have slept for the last day or so.
Cats are valued by society for companionship and the ability to hunt small vermin and household pests.
A common peasant of Neverwinter, this person wears simple clothes and the harried look of someone living in the shadow of plague.
